'''山柰酚'''('''Kaempferol''')是一种天然[[黄酮类化合物|黄酮类化合物]]，是存在于[[茶叶|茶叶]]<ref name="tea">{{cite journal | title = Enzymatic Preparation of Kaempferol from Green Tea Seed and Its Antioxidant Activity | author = Jun Seong Park, Ho Sik Rho, Duck Hee Kim, and Ih Seop Chang | journal = J. Agric. Food Chem. | volume = 54 | issue = 8 | pages = 2951–2956 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16608214| doi = 10.1021/jf052900a}}</ref>、[[西兰花|西兰花]]、[[翠雀草|翠雀草]]、[[金缕梅|金缕梅]]、[[葡萄柚|葡萄柚]]、[[抱子甘藍|抱子甘藍]]、[[苹果|苹果]]等植物中植源性物质。山柰酚为黄色结晶体，熔点为276-278℃，微溶于水，溶于[[乙醇|乙醇]]和[[乙醚|乙醚]]的热混合物中。

== 生物活性 ==
{{medical}}
一些病理学研究已发现，山柰酚的摄取与降低许多疾病的发生率之间存在正相关，如[[癌症|癌症]]和[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]等。大量临床前研究表明，山柰酚和部分[[山柰酚苷|山柰酚苷]]具有广泛的药理活性，包括抗氧化、[[炎症|抗炎]]、[[感染|抗菌]]、[[癌症|抗癌]]、保护[[心脏|心脏]]、保护[[神经|神经]]、[[糖尿病|抗糖尿病]]、[[骨质疏松|抗骨质疏松]]、[[雌激素|抗雌激素]]、[[焦虑|抗焦虑]]、[[疼痛|止痛]]和[[过敏|抗过敏]]等作用。<ref name=minirevmedchem1>{{cite journal|author= Calderon-Montaño JM, Burgos-Moron E, Perez-Guerrero C, Lopez-Lazaro M. |title= A review on the dietary flavonoid kaempferol.|journal=Mini Rev Med Chem.|year=2011|pmid=21428901|volume=11|issue=4|pages=298–344|doi= 10.2174/138955711795305335}}</ref>

[[线叶金合欢|线叶金合欢]]({{small|''Acacia decurrens''}})和[[长叶金合欢|长叶金合欢]]({{small|''Acacia longifolia''}})花朵的黄色即来源于山柰酚。<ref>[http://users.lycaeum.org/~mulga/acacia/phyto.html Lycaeum -- Phytochemistry Intro] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930154547/http://users.lycaeum.org/~mulga/acacia/phyto.html |date=2007-09-30 }}</ref>

一项历时8年的研究发现，山柰酚、[[槲皮素|槲皮素]]和[[杨梅素|杨梅素]]可降低吸烟者患胰腺癌的风险。<ref>Ute Nöthlings, Suzanne P. Murphy, Lynne R. Wilkens, Brian E. Henderson & Laurence N. Kolone. 2007. Flavonols and Pancreatic Cancer Risk. ''American Journal of Epidemiology'' '''166'''(8): 924–931. {{DOI|10.1093/aje/kwm172}}</ref>

山柰酚的摄入亦可降低[[肺癌|肺癌]]的发生率。<ref>{{Cite web | last = Irwin | first = Kim | title = Fruits, vegetables, teas may protect smokers from lung cancer | work = News Releases | publisher = [[UCLA|UCLA]] | url = http://newsroom.ucla.edu/portal/ucla/fruits-vegetables-and-teas-may-51210.aspx | format = HTML | accessdate = 2011-06-17 | date = May 29, 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213144107/http://newsroom.ucla.edu/portal/ucla/fruits-vegetables-and-teas-may-51210.aspx | archive-date = 2012-02-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

